97953.name: Time allocation, average day, women
97953.description:
Average time spent on a particular activity, by women, on an average day. Estimates take a weighted average of minutes spent on a particular activity on weekdays and on the weekend. 

For example, time spent on leisure on an average day is calculated as: 
Leisure_averageday = (5/7)*Leisure_weekday + (2/7)*Leisure_weekend
97953.datasetName: Time use in Sweden - Statistics Sweden

source.name: Statistics Sweden
source.additionalInfo: For the original data, see Table 1 in the 1990 Sweden Statistics time use report; Table B:4 in the 2000 report; and Table B:1a in the 2010 report.
